<p>If you notice any of these symptoms, don't keep running cycles hoping it'll improve - you're just wearing out other components and wasting energy.</p>
<h3>Model-Specific Error Codes We See Daily</h3>
<p>LG's newer models display specific error codes that pinpoint the problem. Code d80 means 80% airflow restriction.</p>
